content: madjin: This month, madjin drove significant feature development and operational improvements within the elizaos/elizaos.github.io repository. They implemented a major new MVP badge system for contributor achievements in PR #161, a substantial effort involving over 4,200 new lines of code. Madjin also enhanced system efficiency by adding adaptive rate limiting (PR #160) and improved the deployment process by creating a new guide (PR #158) and fixing a stats-copying bug (PR #157). Their contributions show a balanced focus across feature work, bug fixes, and documentation, primarily modifying code and configuration files.
